    <!-- Application Structure Plan: A narrative, scrollable infographic that guides the user through the story of Handsaeme Foie Gras. It starts with an introduction to their traditional, vertically-integrated model ("The Artisanal Promise"). It then moves to an analysis of their product offerings and pricing strategy ("The Product Portfolio"). A new Gemini-powered recipe generator is added here. The core conflict is revealed in "The Ethical Crossroads," followed by the critical market event in "The Tipping Point." The analysis culminates in a visual SWOT breakdown ("Strategic Outlook") and concludes with actionable "Recommendations." This narrative flow was chosen to build a compelling story, making the complex business analysis engaging and easy to follow. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 1. Vertical Integration: Goal: Organize. Method: Styled HTML/CSS flexbox flow. Justification: Clearly shows the farm-to-jar process without complex graphics. 2. Price Comparison: Goal: Compare. Method: Bar Chart (Chart.js/Canvas). Justification: Effectively visualizes the vast price-per-kg difference between premium foie gras and accessible pÃ¢tÃ©s, highlighting their market strategy. 3. Gemini Recipe Generator: Goal: Engage & Inspire. Method: Button-triggered API call to Gemini. Justification: Adds an interactive, value-added feature that directly connects the company's products to the end-user in a creative way. 4. Ethical Dilemma: Goal: Compare. Method: Side-by-side styled text cards. Justification: Directly contrasts the marketing claim with the owner's statement, creating a powerful reveal. 5. SWOT Analysis: Goal: Organize. Method: 2x2 colored grid (HTML/CSS). Justification: A classic, instantly recognizable format for strategic analysis. 6. Recommendations: Goal: Organize. Method: Styled list with Unicode icons. Justification: A clear, concise way to present the final strategic advice. -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
